Uttar Pradesh
Dec 10, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 16-year-old girl was allegedly raped by a youth in a farm here when she had gone to attend nature's call, police said today.

The incident took place yesterday when 22-year-old Rahul forcefully took the victim to a farm and raped her, Mavana police station in-charge Parshuram said.

A case has been registered in this regard and the victim has been sent for post mortem, he said, adding, extra police force has been deployed in the village to avoid any tension.

